{"tid":2422721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Stray Kids鉉辰「校暴疑惑」後不參本周《音樂中心》！JYP：正在確認事件真實性","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:14:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3696bd3fd254f9f264a71ff98e82798b0124ed10","tid":2422721,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/25/550_1561887_1614243263.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F25%2F550_1561887_1614243263.webp&h=88f1b814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陷入學暴疑惑的男團Stray Kids成員鉉辰將不參加本週《音樂中心》的演出。<br />\n<br />\n25日，MBC方向媒體表示：「鉉辰將不參加27日播出的《音樂中心》，作爲特別MC的ITZY禮志將出演填補空缺。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/81/f8/3b/81f83bafd3bdab2630a74b6499075dab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F81%2Ff8%2F3b%2F81f83bafd3bdab2630a74b6499075dab.jpg&h=926e62d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此前，在本月22日，有網友於某南韓線上社區中上傳了題爲《暴露Stray Kids黃鉉辰校園暴力》的文章，引起了爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該文章的寫作人介紹自己是中學時期被鉉辰欺負的受害者，並主張：「在鉉辰出道後，當他每次在電視上出現時，我好像都能再次聽到當時莫名其妙的指責和嘲弄，我終於明白了自己沒能抹去那段記憶。」<br />\n<br />\n他還稱：「根本沒想過（鉉辰）會成爲偶像，所以沒有收集證據，只是有學校認證、我的記憶以及同學們的證言。希望不要因爲是年幼而實施的暴力而被正當化，也希望（鉉辰）直接道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，JYP娛樂於23日表示：「正在盡全力確認本話題的真實性。我們正在聽取該成員在問題出現時學校及周邊朋友的意見，如果發帖人允許的話，會考慮直接聽取發帖者的意見。」<br />\n<br />\n「但是，我們確認到現在的無差別擴散的內容中，存在着很多與事實不符的部分，也確認了蓄意生成和上傳惡性謠言的散佈者。對此，我們將通過多種渠道進行詳細調查，查明沒有歪曲的事實關係，對散佈虛假事實的行爲採取法律措施。」<br />\n<br />\n戴個假髮就想呃我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3895a2b176d1e1a4c9c22f9902cd75942823ea","tid":2422721,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"一早話佢似男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6aa0b21eacb3933778626b015cd45fb1dc838e4","tid":2422721,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:46:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4C0ZSZpICVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4C0ZSZpICVA&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=58cf2f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4C0ZSZpICVA</a><br />\n佢兩個勁襯.."},{"pid":"ecffab048797bf749111c25a0a9fb77e3304b8a9","tid":2422721,"uid":78188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:53:33.000Z","msg":"反辰第一人"},{"pid":"e078319503cee20abf5499894478b53aca846e45","tid":2422721,"uid":274500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"佢兩個都幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe31998f6c87664ab25aa9b46065758053611ea5","tid":2422721,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6aa0b21eacb3933778626b015cd45fb1dc838e4","tid":2422721,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:46:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4C0ZSZpICVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4C0ZSZpICVA&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=58cf2f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4C0ZSZpICVA</a><br />\n佢兩個勁襯.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"你係邊狗?"},{"pid":"d0fc064c813b1e6987d5650a5f29aa244c2309a2","tid":2422721,"uid":366032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecffab048797bf749111c25a0a9fb77e3304b8a9","tid":2422721,"uid":78188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:53:33.000Z","msg":"反辰第一人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"反旴第一人"},{"pid":"e7102e39b9d2d391e26f92826568158fd663cdd0","tid":2422721,"uid":7